    /* =====================================================================
     * ARIA menu-button pattern (WAI-ARIA Authoring Practices): role=menu /
     * role=menuitem, aria-controls pairing the trigger to its popup, focus
     * moved into the menu on open, and Arrow Up/Down + Escape keyboard
     * navigation inside the menu.
     *
     * These pin the accessibility fix that completes the previously partial
     * menu pattern (the trigger previously carried only aria-haspopup /
